For loop


for(initialize; condition; changes)
{
    block of code
}


Steps:
1. initialize: create local variables used for iterations
2. condition: check if true
3. execute block
4. changes: any changes to apply
5. go to step 2

any of the initialize, conditiona and changes are optional:

for(;conditon; changes) - if no initialization needed
for(initialization;; changes) - if no condition is needed
for(;;) - infinite loop
